  Parameters:  <none>
  Notes:       
------------------------------------------------------------------------------*/


  EMPTY TEMP-TABLE tt-holdtype.

  RUN Build-Table.

  {&OPEN-QUERY-brUsrGrp}


END PROCEDURE.

